high_descs: Turn around to face the dresser.
Pick up the newspaper from the top of the dresser.
Turn around and walk to the desklamp on the left.
Switch on the desklamp and examine the newspaper.
anns.task_desc: Examine the newspaper under the DeskLamp.

high_descs: Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the coffee table.
Pick up newspaper from the coffee table.
Go left and head straight towards the wall. After that, turn left and walk straight into the room, turning to the desk lamp on your right.
anns.task_desc: Examine a newspaper by the light of a desk lamp.

high_descs: Turn around, move towards the coffee table.
Take the news paper from the coffee table.
Turn around, turn left, move towards the wall, take right towards the desk lamp.
anns.task_desc: To take the news paper from the coffee table, put the desk lamp on.
